title: PANIC @: Watch Musician/Comedian Emily Panic Goof Around at BUKU Music + Art Project
text: Now watching: Watch Musician/Comedian Emily Panic Goof Around at BUKU Music + Art Project At BUKU in New Orleans, Emily Panic asks festival goers about ghosts, learns a few new moves, and plays Never Have I Ever.
